headline: 2 Top Tech Stocks That Can Double by 2030
summary: Nvidia continues to meet insatiable demand for AI chips in the data center market.  Lam Research is seeing its addressable chip market expand as AI-based demand continues to grow.  Investing in innovative technology leaders can help you build wealth over the long term.
